(firstQuint)Acupuncture for Body Weight Control.

 This is a pilot single-blind, randomized, sham-controlled trial.

 72 participants will be randomly assigned to acupuncture group or control group.

 The duration of the treatment will be 8 weeks with 2 sessions per week and the follow-up period will be 8 weeks.

